Value: Pentanet Limited operates as a telecommunications carrier and internet service provider in Perth, Australia. It operates in two segments, Internet and Telecommunication Services, and Gaming Technology. The company offers fixed-wireless network services to residential and business customers. It also provides a range of fixed-line internet services including national broadband network, local broadband network, PentaMAX, XFIBRE, and apartment broadband products, as well as offers Wi-Fi setup services, and business and commercial solutions. Pentanet Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Balcatta, Australia.
